{% block content %}

<h1 class="Article-title">Size</h1>
<p class="c-Text--lead">Responsive component for determining widths</p>

  <p>A utility object that can be combined with other objects to determine widths using a <strong>12 column grid</strong></p>

<hr>

<h2 id="section:usage"><a href="#section:usage" class="c-Text--resetLink">Usage</a></h2>

<h3>Settings</h3>

<p>In <code>/stylesheets/settings/_settings.grid.scss</code> you can choose your gutter size.</p>

<h3>Classes</h3>
<table class="c-Table c-Table--striped c-Text--left" width="100%">
  <thead>
  <tr>
    <th class="o-Size--4">Class</th>
    <th>Description</th>
  </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
  <tr>
    <th>o-Size--full</th>
    <td>Fills 100% of the available width</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>o-Size--1</th>
    <td>One grid cell of 12</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>o-Size--11</th>
    <td>Eleven grid cells of 12</td>
  </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

