<h3>Responsive modifiers</h3>

<p>The 12/16 column grid is also available at all the different breakpoints (except xxs).</p>

<table class="c-Table c-Text--left" width="100%">
  <thead>
  <tr>
    <th class="o-Size--1of3">Class</th>
    <th>Description</th>
  </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
  <tr>
    <th>o-Size@xs--full</th>
    <td>Fills 100% of the available width from 'xs' and upwards</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>o-Size@sm--6</th>
    <td>Six grid cells of 12 from 'sm' and upwards</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>o-Size@xl--12of16</th>
    <td>Twelve grid cells of 16 from 'xl' and upwards</td>
  </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

